WEBVTT

00:07.801 --> 00:10.581
Recently, Youting sent some gifts

00:10.601 --> 00:12.390
to the noblemen and officials

00:12.391 --> 00:15.451
during the Mid-Autumn Festival.

00:15.521 --> 00:18.581
Even Minister Dou
has accepted his gifts,

00:18.801 --> 00:20.171
and they seem close.

00:20.721 --> 00:21.861
What do you think?

00:24.351 --> 00:26.421
I shall not talk bad
about our key ministers.

00:26.561 --> 00:29.451
Moreover, we need the rice
from Lizhen in the north.

00:29.961 --> 00:31.120
Minister Dou

00:31.121 --> 00:33.680
is the only one in the palace
who can speak their language.

00:33.681 --> 00:35.451
He has immense power in politics.

00:36.271 --> 00:38.661
If we denounce him
simply because of that,

00:39.151 --> 00:40.981
the people in Liaodong would be rattled.

00:41.801 --> 00:46.251
Aren't you worried that Lord Qing
and Dou Shishu may work together

00:46.681 --> 00:49.531
to weaken your influence
as the Crown Prince?

00:50.281 --> 00:51.701
Father, you are unwell now.

00:51.831 --> 00:54.661
It would be disloyal of me
to fight with my brother now.

00:54.691 --> 00:57.941
This may also lead to speculation
among the officials

00:58.121 --> 00:59.891
that we are trying to remove dissidents,

01:00.041 --> 01:03.101
which will in turn cause
a public uproar.

01:11.031 --> 01:12.381
You've grown sensible.

01:12.871 --> 01:14.051
However, remember this.

01:14.361 --> 01:17.611
You cannot clap with just one hand.

01:18.391 --> 01:19.941
You should learn from your brother

01:20.871 --> 01:22.440
about being a ruler

01:22.441 --> 01:24.171
and gaining your subordinates' support.

01:28.801 --> 01:30.101
I apologize for my foolishness.

01:30.671 --> 01:32.280
All I know is to improve myself

01:32.281 --> 01:33.861
and love my country and people.

01:34.291 --> 01:35.941
I've spent so many years working hard

01:36.511 --> 01:38.891
to become a good Crown Prince,

01:38.921 --> 01:40.061
hoping to bring honor

01:41.721 --> 01:43.611
to our ancestors and kingdom.

01:46.231 --> 01:47.371
You may leave now.

02:05.391 --> 02:07.531
What do you think of the Crown Prince?

02:11.761 --> 02:13.390
I wouldn't dare comment anything

02:13.391 --> 02:15.941
about the Crown Prince.

02:16.641 --> 02:18.851
You watched him grow up.

02:20.271 --> 02:23.811
He may seem proud and quiet,

02:24.321 --> 02:25.971
but he has a benevolent heart.

02:26.481 --> 02:28.221
Every year, on my birthday,

02:28.391 --> 02:29.830
everyone else tries to impress me

02:29.831 --> 02:31.920
by offering precious treasures,

02:31.921 --> 02:33.181
but he would instead

02:33.641 --> 02:35.950
gather locusts, seedlings,

02:35.951 --> 02:37.710
and cloths from all over the kingdom.

02:37.711 --> 02:39.600
He doesn't even know
how to maintain a facade.

02:39.601 --> 02:41.661
How will he gain
the support of the officials?

02:42.231 --> 02:44.251
I don't know if I should
blame Liang Jifang

02:44.271 --> 02:47.501
for teaching him too well, or teaching him
until he's grown foolish.

02:47.831 --> 02:49.411
I understand your worries, Your Majesty.

02:49.921 --> 02:52.291
The Crown Prince is morally upright.

02:52.671 --> 02:55.571
There will be good officials
who will stay loyal to him.

02:55.921 --> 02:59.291
Yousheng is the Crown Prince

03:00.111 --> 03:01.781
and my son.

03:02.681 --> 03:04.691
It's time for him to learn

03:07.321 --> 03:10.221
how to use his best weapon, Yantang.

04:31.261 --> 04:35.500
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

04:35.501 --> 04:38.761
=Episode 27=

04:40.741 --> 04:42.601
(Yizhi Hall)

04:44.191 --> 04:46.051
So, the Crown Prince wasn't trying

04:46.631 --> 04:48.430
to win your favor, but he's been

04:48.431 --> 04:49.661
spying and warning you.

04:50.721 --> 04:52.310
All the Crown Prince wants

04:52.311 --> 04:53.731
is to protect his kingdom.

04:54.071 --> 04:56.461
He's taking his role
as the next emperor seriously.

04:56.671 --> 04:58.291
He's not the mastermind.

05:01.361 --> 05:02.931
If the Crown Prince loses support,

05:03.361 --> 05:05.851
and Lord Qing wants to seize the throne,

05:06.841 --> 05:08.021
what would he do?

05:08.671 --> 05:11.221
First, he needs military support.

05:11.801 --> 05:13.310
The ministers in charge of the troops

05:13.311 --> 05:14.631
have always sided with Lord Qing.

05:14.641 --> 05:16.480
Moreover, there's a new
horse market in Liaodong,

05:16.481 --> 05:17.720
making it a major trading hub
at the borders.

05:17.721 --> 05:19.491
They'll be able to grow
their troops easily.

05:19.911 --> 05:22.171
Now that Dou Shishu has control
over the Ministry of War,

05:22.451 --> 05:25.141
he has the power to deploy the
kingdom's troops in any way he wants.

05:25.921 --> 05:27.531
If he supports Lord Qing,

05:27.631 --> 05:29.491
he could launch a coup easily

05:29.601 --> 05:30.670
and attack the capital.

05:30.671 --> 05:32.161
(Capital, Shengtian Court)

05:32.481 --> 05:33.480
Also,

05:33.481 --> 05:34.971
before he launches a coup,

05:35.431 --> 05:38.221
he needs to make sure the ministers
can keep this a secret.

05:38.231 --> 05:40.781
To do that, he will need support
from the civilian ministers

05:41.311 --> 05:42.851
to stabilize the political situation.

05:43.401 --> 05:44.661
You're right.

05:44.921 --> 05:46.291
Other than my fifth uncle

05:46.631 --> 05:48.781
and the other key ministers,

05:49.041 --> 05:52.101
there must be many people
who are secretly supporting Lord Qing.

05:53.601 --> 05:55.461
I've heard from Mr. Chen

05:55.801 --> 05:57.750
that Mu Chuan became
the Minister of Works

05:57.751 --> 05:59.491
because he had
the support of Empress Wan.

06:01.871 --> 06:03.731
Apart from military power
and the royal court,

06:04.031 --> 06:06.701
he also needs to seize control
of the palace and capital's reserves,

06:07.041 --> 06:09.411
such as the Imperial Guards
stationed at the palace itself.

06:10.311 --> 06:12.160
If we look at history, both Wei Lue

06:12.161 --> 06:14.021
and Tang Shu's coups were successful

06:14.551 --> 06:16.051
because they got the Imperial Guards

06:16.071 --> 06:17.731
to deliver the fatal blow.

06:18.631 --> 06:21.221
So, no matter where they
start launching their coup,

06:21.231 --> 06:22.451
they will have to go past you.

06:23.751 --> 06:25.901
That's why they planned
the bandit invasion,

06:25.911 --> 06:29.101
so they could replace the capital's military
reserves with their own people.

06:29.481 --> 06:31.931
By then, they could easily

06:32.071 --> 06:34.461
open the city gates

06:35.161 --> 06:36.611
or imprison His Majesty.

06:37.601 --> 06:40.661
Among the eunuchs,
other than the two Eunuch Wangs,

06:41.041 --> 06:44.411
there are another six to seven eunuchs
who hold power.

06:44.721 --> 06:46.400
But if we investigate them one by one,

06:46.401 --> 06:48.141
we might alert them.

06:49.231 --> 06:50.630
The Crown Prince has always

06:50.631 --> 06:52.171
behaved like an ascetic,

06:52.431 --> 06:54.221
and I don't really know
what he's thinking.

06:54.231 --> 06:56.491
However, if he knows
about Lord Qing's ambitions,

06:57.751 --> 06:59.901
I wonder if he'd panically confront him,

07:00.071 --> 07:03.411
or secretly plot against him.

07:04.921 --> 07:08.021
Why don't we test him?

07:09.751 --> 07:12.531
Lord Qing has a bigger chance
of winning.

07:12.631 --> 07:14.821
Still, if we support Lord Qing,

07:15.431 --> 07:17.781
even if he does become the Emperor,

07:18.631 --> 07:21.261
that doesn't make him
any less of a thief and a traitor.

07:21.431 --> 07:22.931
The results are bound to be ugly

07:23.801 --> 07:25.221
whether he succeeds or not.

07:28.751 --> 07:29.891
What's wrong?

07:29.901 --> 07:31.174
(Qiguang Wanfo Pagoda)
Your Highness,

07:31.175 --> 07:33.400
(Qiguang Wanfo Pagoda)
the throne isn't yours yet,

07:33.401 --> 07:36.141
and you're already eager to kill
those who supported you?

07:45.231 --> 07:46.371
Don't worry.

07:47.041 --> 07:48.821
I know what to do.

07:49.111 --> 07:52.051
I will not make you suffer
because of my loyalties.

07:58.311 --> 08:00.731
My uncle is helping Lord Qing
to collude with other ministers

08:01.751 --> 08:02.920
to steal the throne.

08:02.921 --> 08:05.901
If proven guilty,
he will be a horrendous sinner.

08:07.361 --> 08:09.960
My grandmother, my father, and even me

08:09.961 --> 08:11.291
will be prosecuted.

08:12.631 --> 08:15.261
Empress Wan was so eager
to arrange our marriage

08:16.191 --> 08:18.021
probably to set the stage up

08:18.281 --> 08:20.171
and use you as a bait.

08:22.601 --> 08:23.781
The Art of War states

08:24.101 --> 08:27.101
that there are five dangerous faults
can lead to the downfall of a general.

08:27.111 --> 08:28.411
The most dangerous one

08:28.481 --> 08:30.781
is being overly compassionate,

08:30.961 --> 08:32.851
which leads to
constant worry and trouble.

08:33.281 --> 08:35.731
In some cases, the enemy
captures the loved ones

08:35.881 --> 08:37.541
of the opposing party as hostage,

08:37.551 --> 08:39.221
forcing them to surrender
without a fight.

08:39.921 --> 08:41.061
I am nowhere

08:42.161 --> 08:43.421
as ruthless as Dou Shishu.

08:44.761 --> 08:46.821
I won't be held hostage by anyone.

08:47.121 --> 08:48.611
I have a mind of my own.

08:49.161 --> 08:50.731
I don't take threats from anyone.

08:51.491 --> 08:54.011
I won't repeat the mistakes
of my mother and the Duke of Ding.

08:55.881 --> 08:57.251
What they couldn't achieve,

08:57.471 --> 08:58.611
we will.

09:01.401 --> 09:02.541
Very well.

09:03.671 --> 09:04.880
I'll dye your hair

09:04.881 --> 09:06.731
every month so that

09:07.471 --> 09:09.950
you won't become

09:09.951 --> 09:11.251
a white-haired imp.

09:12.921 --> 09:14.131
Deal.

09:24.351 --> 09:26.160
Madam, you've always
been good with crafts.

09:26.161 --> 09:28.061
That new pattern looks pretty.

09:29.921 --> 09:31.081
Madam!

09:31.361 --> 09:32.501
Madam!

09:32.831 --> 09:34.941
Madam , bad news!

09:35.801 --> 09:38.070
Grand Princess Shude
sent an urgent letter

09:38.071 --> 09:40.371
saying that she has
a dreadful emergency!

09:40.401 --> 09:41.701
What happened?

09:43.521 --> 09:44.661
She needs another player.

09:54.501 --> 09:57.641
(Ningshou Palace)

10:03.401 --> 10:04.520
Dou Zhao.

10:04.521 --> 10:07.421
If Her Majesty didn't remind me,

10:07.641 --> 10:08.800
I almost forgot

10:08.801 --> 10:10.491
that we could invite you for mahjong.

10:11.761 --> 10:13.251
This is the Empress.

10:15.001 --> 10:16.221
And the Crown Princess.

10:18.191 --> 10:19.701
Greetings, Your Majesty.

10:20.001 --> 10:21.341
Greetings, Your Highness.

10:22.881 --> 10:25.771
I've heard that the Duchess of Ying
is a successful businesswoman.

10:25.951 --> 10:28.301
You are a model to the kingdom's women.

10:28.531 --> 10:29.710
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

10:29.711 --> 10:31.061
You're just in time.

10:31.401 --> 10:33.101
We need another player for mahjong.

10:34.001 --> 10:35.371
Let's begin now.

10:36.281 --> 10:37.421
Come in.

10:40.641 --> 10:41.920
I hope that Your Majesty

10:41.921 --> 10:43.520
and Your Highnesses

10:43.521 --> 10:45.011
won't mind me if I fumble.

10:47.831 --> 10:48.971
Nine.

10:50.161 --> 10:52.421
I wonder how lucky I will be today.

10:52.471 --> 10:54.491
Luck doesn't matter.

10:54.801 --> 10:57.101
Winning is all about tactics.

10:57.921 --> 10:59.421
A good game depends

10:59.761 --> 11:01.581
on the person playing.

11:02.711 --> 11:03.800
If you want to win,

11:03.801 --> 11:07.181
you need to see
who's playing against whom.

11:08.471 --> 11:09.771
You have a point, Mother.

11:09.951 --> 11:11.771
That's how games are.

11:12.041 --> 11:14.301
Someone wins, and someone loses.

11:15.161 --> 11:18.101
Sometimes, wins and losses
are not determined in a split second.

11:19.521 --> 11:20.661
Thirty thousand.

11:31.191 --> 11:32.331
I win.

11:33.431 --> 11:34.851
Seventy thousand.

11:36.431 --> 11:37.551
I can't believe this.

11:37.561 --> 11:39.191
Come on, let's play
another eight rounds.

11:39.201 --> 11:40.851
We'll see if you're really that lucky.

11:41.311 --> 11:43.181
I just lucked out.

11:43.761 --> 11:45.101
Mother, you're still

11:45.191 --> 11:46.851
the star player here.

11:47.281 --> 11:48.491
(Eight rounds?)

11:48.951 --> 11:50.371
(Against the Grand Princess,)

11:50.431 --> 11:51.611
(the Empress)

11:52.121 --> 11:53.651
(and the Crown Princess?)

11:54.241 --> 11:55.941
(This isn't a game.)

11:55.951 --> 11:57.701
(This is a landmine!)

12:03.521 --> 12:04.771
I win!

12:05.191 --> 12:06.971
This is so fun.

12:07.711 --> 12:08.640
Still, Dou Zhao.

12:08.641 --> 12:10.731
It seems like you're unlucky today.

12:12.241 --> 12:13.971
You've never won even once.

12:14.431 --> 12:15.701
My dear Duchess,

12:15.921 --> 12:17.491
did you go easy on us?

12:18.951 --> 12:20.491
I just learned how to play mahjong,

12:20.711 --> 12:22.541
so I'm not very good at it.

12:26.671 --> 12:28.760
Back when the Duke of Ying
went to Liaodong

12:28.761 --> 12:31.181
to help the Jiang clan settle down,

12:31.521 --> 12:35.731
I heard that he
hit it off with Lord Qing

12:35.921 --> 12:37.581
right after they met.

12:40.401 --> 12:42.880
Yantang did request His Highness

12:42.881 --> 12:45.160
so that the elder folks in the clan

12:45.161 --> 12:46.120
could get treated,

12:46.121 --> 12:48.891
and that the leaking roofs
could be fixed.

12:49.951 --> 12:51.800
That's typical of him.

12:51.801 --> 12:53.800
He's a loyal citizen.

12:53.801 --> 12:56.651
To do that, you need to be loyal
to your family first.

12:56.671 --> 12:58.350
I raised Youting

12:58.351 --> 12:59.830
until he was 12 years old,

12:59.831 --> 13:01.651
and he was deployed to the barren lands.

13:01.731 --> 13:03.830
He never received any education
from famous scholars,

13:03.831 --> 13:06.251
but he was still respected
by the court officials.

13:07.161 --> 13:09.070
Nevertheless, it's only because

13:09.071 --> 13:11.771
they admired his loyalty to the kingdom.

13:18.121 --> 13:19.160
Five dots.

13:19.161 --> 13:20.301
I win.

13:22.871 --> 13:24.830
You're a clever lady, Duchess.

13:24.831 --> 13:26.221
You're good at mahjong.

13:35.391 --> 13:37.070
Madam, I thought
you were playing mahjong?

13:37.071 --> 13:38.550
Why do you look so lethargic?

13:38.551 --> 13:40.371
I've been playing since noon till now.

13:41.001 --> 13:41.950
I didn't know

13:41.951 --> 13:44.011
they're so enthusiastic when they play.

13:44.431 --> 13:47.251
It's not a simple game.

13:47.641 --> 13:49.221
Who won the most?

13:49.541 --> 13:50.800
Judging from the number of wins,

13:50.801 --> 13:52.221
it's the Empress, of course.

13:53.801 --> 13:55.011
Your Ladyship.

13:56.001 --> 13:57.760
Her Majesty wants to see you.

13:57.761 --> 14:00.181
Please head to Kunning Palace now.

14:08.951 --> 14:10.550
My pleasure.

14:10.551 --> 14:11.771
Lead the way.

14:12.001 --> 14:13.141
This way.

14:21.081 --> 14:22.760
Your Majesty,
the Duchess of Ying is here.

14:22.761 --> 14:24.830
- Your Majesty.
- Finally, help is here.

14:24.831 --> 14:27.181
Here, take a look at these papers.

14:27.191 --> 14:29.661
Lately, the Emperor wants
to reduce the palace's expenditure,

14:29.671 --> 14:33.181
which covers everything from clothes
and rewards to even papers.

14:33.431 --> 14:34.851
Here, look at this.

14:47.681 --> 14:50.331
The palace uses more than nine million
pieces of papers every year.

14:50.341 --> 14:52.651
Half of them are used
for books and records.

14:53.281 --> 14:55.240
While bamboo and jute are cheaper,

14:55.241 --> 14:57.461
they tend to rot easily,
which makes them hard to store.

14:57.591 --> 14:59.181
You could opt for papyrus instead.

14:59.891 --> 15:02.181
If there's a papyrus factory
near the capital,

15:02.191 --> 15:03.371
you could simplify the process

15:03.761 --> 15:05.371
and save up to 40% in costs.

15:06.241 --> 15:08.301
If you use recycled paper,

15:08.671 --> 15:09.821
you could save even more.

15:10.241 --> 15:11.651
You do know a lot.

15:11.921 --> 15:13.771
You're a great help to me.

15:14.881 --> 15:16.021
You flatter me, Your Majesty.

15:16.921 --> 15:19.061
You're such a demure lady

15:19.161 --> 15:20.400
and a clever merchant,

15:20.401 --> 15:22.590
while the Duke is both
strong and courageous,

15:22.591 --> 15:23.720
defending the kingdom.

15:23.721 --> 15:26.941
He will be able to protect
our kingdom if stationed at Liaodong.

15:28.401 --> 15:30.181
Unfortunately, he's ill now.

15:30.951 --> 15:32.581
Thank you for your concern,
Your Majesty.

15:33.281 --> 15:35.971
In Liaodong, there's a snow lingzhi
that grows every 300 years.

15:36.281 --> 15:38.701
They say it can even resurrect the dead.

15:39.001 --> 15:40.400
This is a Xueyuan pill

15:40.401 --> 15:42.731
that contains snow lingzhi.

15:44.071 --> 15:47.131
I'm sure you're good at medicine,

15:47.241 --> 15:50.061
so why don't you try whether this pill
is as miraculous as they claim?

15:51.311 --> 15:52.830
Lord Shi

15:52.831 --> 15:55.181
wanted to give this to the Duke too,

15:55.351 --> 15:57.120
but he didn't even look at it,

15:57.121 --> 15:59.731
and shooed Lord Shi out right away.

15:59.961 --> 16:02.240
I know as his wife, you should
respect the Duke's wishes,

16:02.241 --> 16:04.240
but, Your Ladyship,

16:04.241 --> 16:06.941
can you really see him die?

16:11.831 --> 16:14.821
Your niece is a clever lady.

16:15.521 --> 16:17.941
I'd love to help her too.

16:18.801 --> 16:20.541
She is indeed capable.

16:20.751 --> 16:22.891
Even those who never
involve themselves in politics

16:23.311 --> 16:25.221
are in this mess thanks to her.

16:25.361 --> 16:28.371
You're the one who
dragged me into this mess.

16:30.191 --> 16:33.251
The entire palace knows
I recommended you to become minister.

16:33.551 --> 16:34.891
Now that you're helping Lord Qing,

16:34.951 --> 16:37.341
the officials and
the Emperor would think

16:37.431 --> 16:41.251
that I also support Lord Qing
in seizing the throne.

16:44.801 --> 16:46.581
I am part of the royal family.

16:46.721 --> 16:49.181
You should know where my bottom line is.

16:49.881 --> 16:51.461
Whatever you're doing,

16:52.001 --> 16:53.141
stop.

16:54.551 --> 16:55.550
I can't.

16:55.551 --> 16:57.461
You're not listening to me anymore?

16:59.061 --> 17:00.070
Calm down, Your Highness.

17:00.071 --> 17:02.000
Don't kneel if I didn't ask you to.

17:02.001 --> 17:04.120
As your servant, I am obliged to kneel.

17:04.121 --> 17:05.960
Life is like swimming
against the currents.

17:05.961 --> 17:08.451
You have to abandon
everything unimportant

17:08.761 --> 17:10.301
to be able to swim upwards.

17:11.801 --> 17:14.101
That's what you taught me.

17:16.071 --> 17:18.371
When did I teach you that?

17:20.041 --> 17:22.741
Back when I was an assistant magistrate
in Dengzhou,

17:22.761 --> 17:24.171
I was still a lowly official

17:25.051 --> 17:26.981
with no prestigious background.

17:27.041 --> 17:28.181
All those years,

17:28.831 --> 17:31.021
I wasn't treated like a human.

17:31.151 --> 17:32.741
Those crooks treated me

17:32.761 --> 17:34.261
like a doormat.

17:34.721 --> 17:36.931
I worked hard every day and night,

17:36.961 --> 17:38.630
and they took my credit

17:38.631 --> 17:40.371
to rise through the official ranks,

17:41.481 --> 17:43.371
yet I was still the doormat.

17:43.591 --> 17:44.731
So,

17:45.181 --> 17:47.341
I wanted to resign and retake
the imperial examination,

17:48.801 --> 17:50.541
but they wouldn't let me do that.

17:53.281 --> 17:57.741
Back then, my old husband just died.

17:59.001 --> 18:01.501
On the day I went to pray for him,

18:02.391 --> 18:04.981
you wrote me a hymn,

18:06.551 --> 18:09.261
and I promoted you in return.

18:10.391 --> 18:12.851
Now, you're already a key minister.

18:14.911 --> 18:16.611
Isn't that enough?

18:18.911 --> 18:20.851
I loved the hymn you wrote for me.

18:22.561 --> 18:24.381
What can I do for you?

18:24.761 --> 18:27.331
I only hope to resign my post

18:27.341 --> 18:29.581
and retake the imperial examination
to earn a better rank

18:29.591 --> 18:32.101
and be assigned to a place
where I can unleash my talents.

18:32.731 --> 18:34.341
Such a place doesn't exist.

18:36.021 --> 18:39.211
I wrote a letter of recommendation
for you to the Ministry of Personnel.

18:39.441 --> 18:42.861
Next month, you will
be the Magistrate of Haiyan.

18:43.911 --> 18:45.310
I only wish to rely on myself...

18:45.311 --> 18:48.101
Taking shortcuts is not something
to be shameful of.

18:48.721 --> 18:50.451
Your dignity and principles

18:51.311 --> 18:53.411
shouldn't be within
your consideration now.

18:54.491 --> 18:56.181
I've abandoned so many things.

18:57.641 --> 18:59.540
They said I was a brown-noser

18:59.541 --> 19:00.960
with no shame,

19:00.961 --> 19:02.341
but I didn't care.

19:02.911 --> 19:04.521
I just wanted to see

19:05.041 --> 19:07.060
how far I could go

19:07.061 --> 19:08.310
along the shortcut I took

19:08.311 --> 19:10.251
in exchange for my principles.

19:10.441 --> 19:12.310
And I will go as far as it takes me.

19:12.311 --> 19:13.851
My family

19:14.311 --> 19:16.261
used to be mere peddlers.

19:16.931 --> 19:18.201
It was me

19:18.451 --> 19:21.301
who made us a prestigious clan.

19:21.911 --> 19:23.101
Shishu.

19:24.071 --> 19:26.280
I sacrificed my marriage

19:26.281 --> 19:28.171
for wealth and freedom.

19:29.071 --> 19:31.341
However, I didn't harm anyone.

19:31.911 --> 19:34.691
The path you're taking is too risky.

19:35.391 --> 19:37.150
You will harm yourself

19:37.151 --> 19:38.891
and me.

19:44.201 --> 19:45.341
Your Highness.

19:45.761 --> 19:47.131
You have my support.

19:48.201 --> 19:49.341
Someday,

19:50.241 --> 19:51.851
I will give you

19:53.041 --> 19:54.581
everything you've wanted.

20:06.261 --> 20:07.401
You're back.

20:08.391 --> 20:09.931
Where did you get this Xueyuan pill?

20:11.551 --> 20:13.261
From the Empress.

20:17.831 --> 20:20.910
She's offering me this so-called antidote
to make me one of her cronies.

20:20.911 --> 20:21.820
You know very well

20:21.821 --> 20:23.891
that I'd never disregard
my principles to survive.

20:24.311 --> 20:25.581
I know.

20:25.871 --> 20:27.541
You want to avenge your family.

20:28.481 --> 20:29.720
But, this pill is so rare

20:29.721 --> 20:31.720
that Mr. Chen couldn't find it anywhere.

20:31.721 --> 20:33.821
Now that the pill
is right in front of you,

20:33.961 --> 20:35.411
why don't you try it?

20:35.421 --> 20:37.851
The Empress and Lord Qing
is taking advantage of my illness.

20:38.091 --> 20:39.730
If the pill works

20:39.731 --> 20:41.280
and prolongs my life,

20:41.281 --> 20:44.071
it'd be harder for both of us to say goodbye
when my condition worsens.

20:44.081 --> 20:46.581
By then, we'd want to get another pill,
and another afterwards.

20:46.591 --> 20:48.550
We'd be at the Empress bidding.

20:48.551 --> 20:51.341
We can solve these problems as they come.

20:51.551 --> 20:53.261
As long as there's a glimmer of hope,

20:53.391 --> 20:54.910
I want you to live.

20:54.911 --> 20:56.821
That's exactly what
the Empress is planning.

20:57.071 --> 20:58.350
She wants us to side

20:58.351 --> 20:59.691
with Lord Qing.

21:00.201 --> 21:03.021
I know the Empress
is plotting something.

21:03.071 --> 21:04.651
Don't worry, though.

21:05.201 --> 21:06.341
I got this pill

21:06.351 --> 21:07.821
by stealing it.

21:08.521 --> 21:09.661
You stole it?

21:11.201 --> 21:13.480
I managed to find out
that Lord Qing was planning

21:13.481 --> 21:15.531
to deliver some precious gifts
to the Empress today,

21:15.541 --> 21:17.261
which includes the Xueyuan pill.

21:20.071 --> 21:21.211
Beat him up!

21:21.531 --> 21:22.390
Take everything away!

21:22.391 --> 21:23.891
It might be valuable!

21:24.311 --> 21:25.741
Come on!

21:28.681 --> 21:30.741
I don't want to side with Lord Qing,

21:31.201 --> 21:33.371
but I also want my husband to live.

21:34.001 --> 21:35.141
I'm sorry, Ms. Longevity.

21:35.391 --> 21:37.061
I was wrong to accuse you.

21:38.651 --> 21:42.211
In the past, I ignored everything
to discover the truth

21:42.671 --> 21:43.811
and avenge my family.

21:44.181 --> 21:45.941
But now, you gave me a family.

21:46.181 --> 21:47.821
I am no longer alone.

21:50.351 --> 21:51.310
I promise you this.

21:51.311 --> 21:52.451
In the future,

21:52.521 --> 21:54.131
even if I had to sacrifice something,

21:55.041 --> 21:56.821
I'd protect this family.

22:01.391 --> 22:02.741
I'll take the pill now.

22:09.731 --> 22:12.211
Back then, he was already
on Lord Qing's side,

22:12.481 --> 22:14.061
so he must have taken the Xueyuan pill.

22:14.241 --> 22:17.651
However, his hair was white,
and he was still poisoned.

22:19.351 --> 22:20.491
Wait.

22:22.071 --> 22:23.211
Su Lan.

22:24.071 --> 22:24.920
Madam.

22:24.921 --> 22:26.130
Get me some warm water

22:26.131 --> 22:27.411
and my medicine box.

22:27.521 --> 22:28.661
Yes.

22:30.441 --> 22:31.581
Are you suspecting

22:32.351 --> 22:33.851
that something's wrong with this pill?

22:50.201 --> 22:52.171
Poisoned blood should be
purplish black in color.

22:52.681 --> 22:53.821
If this antidote works,

22:54.281 --> 22:55.691
the blood should react to it.

23:00.111 --> 23:01.251
Look.

23:01.441 --> 23:02.581
The color's changing!

23:02.681 --> 23:04.651
That means the antidote works.

23:11.311 --> 23:12.451
Ms. Longevity!

23:12.481 --> 23:13.621
Zhangru?

23:13.761 --> 23:15.061
Ms. Longevity!

23:16.351 --> 23:17.581
What brings you back?

23:17.591 --> 23:19.291
I thought you're visiting
Uncle in Diannan?

23:19.301 --> 23:20.451
Why are you back?

23:20.711 --> 23:21.960
The Mid-Autumn Festival is here.

23:21.961 --> 23:23.350
I'm back to celebrate.

23:23.351 --> 23:24.611
Have you forgotten?

23:25.631 --> 23:27.910
You've never been so enthusiastic

23:27.911 --> 23:29.891
about a festival.

23:32.631 --> 23:33.891
Don't tell me

23:34.041 --> 23:35.501
someone's celebrating with you today.

23:36.801 --> 23:38.071
No.

23:38.081 --> 23:39.480
The lantern parade is starting soon.

23:39.481 --> 23:41.061
Why are you still cooped up here?

23:41.151 --> 23:42.741
I'm going to the parade now.

23:46.961 --> 23:48.101
Come on.

23:48.521 --> 23:49.661
Let's take a look.

23:55.281 --> 23:57.371
To think we were robbed

23:57.441 --> 23:59.611
right inside the palace.

24:00.241 --> 24:01.981
What a joke.

24:03.311 --> 24:05.581
The bandits seemed to be
remnants of Cangbei Gang.

24:06.311 --> 24:08.691
We have already
eliminated the entire gang.

24:09.071 --> 24:11.550
Besides, this is too much
of a coincidence.

24:11.551 --> 24:13.821
The Xueyuan pill was also stolen.

24:17.681 --> 24:19.211
Could it be Dou Zhao?

24:19.631 --> 24:20.771
No.

24:21.481 --> 24:22.440
She looked so firm

24:22.441 --> 24:24.131
when she rejected me.

24:25.351 --> 24:27.611
Since she had already refused you,

24:27.711 --> 24:30.951
why do they have to go through
the trouble to steal it?

24:31.201 --> 24:34.501
Looks like they're just plain robbers.

24:34.601 --> 24:36.691
They must be more than mere robbers.

24:39.311 --> 24:41.341
Dou Zhao is a sly woman.

24:41.961 --> 24:43.371
It must be her.

24:43.481 --> 24:45.110
How dare she oppose us?

24:45.111 --> 24:46.301
Why don't I send someone

24:46.311 --> 24:47.680
to bring Dou Zhao here right away?

24:47.681 --> 24:48.821
No.

24:49.481 --> 24:51.110
We have no proof now.

24:51.111 --> 24:52.451
We can't do anything to her.

24:54.391 --> 24:56.211
Since we can't be allies,

24:56.801 --> 24:59.341
we'll have to be foes.

25:00.441 --> 25:02.120
Hot buns fresh from the oven!
Take a look!

25:02.121 --> 25:03.341
Lantern quizzes available here!

25:03.591 --> 25:04.870
Want to take a quiz?

25:04.871 --> 25:05.910
It's two wen for a guess.

25:05.911 --> 25:07.601
If you get it right,
you'll get a lantern.

25:17.001 --> 25:20.131
"At the end of the year,
there's fish and rice."

25:21.001 --> 25:23.021
I can read it out,

25:23.441 --> 25:25.261
but I don't understand.

25:30.631 --> 25:31.720
It's the character "lin".

25:31.721 --> 25:32.861
"Lin"?

25:32.961 --> 25:34.101
Let's see.

25:34.381 --> 25:35.440
("Lin")

25:35.441 --> 25:36.870
It really is.

25:36.871 --> 25:38.390
Officer Chen, I didn't know

25:38.391 --> 25:39.531
you're also good at quizzes.

25:41.041 --> 25:42.581
Here's your lantern.

25:43.071 --> 25:44.310
How cute.

25:44.311 --> 25:45.601
It's a rabbit.

25:46.001 --> 25:47.251
It's so cute.

25:47.831 --> 25:48.971
Look.

25:53.341 --> 25:54.501
Do you like this lantern?

26:01.071 --> 26:02.261
Yes.

26:07.801 --> 26:08.941
Ms. Longevity.

26:20.811 --> 26:21.951
What is it?

26:22.721 --> 26:24.150
I feel like we're being followed.

26:24.151 --> 26:25.291
Who?

26:33.201 --> 26:34.651
Perhaps I was worrying for nothing.

26:35.001 --> 26:36.141
Let's go.

26:39.151 --> 26:40.520
Why did you pull me?

26:40.521 --> 26:41.781
Don't try to cheat.

26:42.001 --> 26:43.310
We had a deal.

26:43.311 --> 26:45.101
If you disturb them,

26:45.311 --> 26:46.541
that'd be counted as cheating.

26:46.681 --> 26:48.651
I wasn't trying to disturb them.

26:49.591 --> 26:51.501
I just don't want to lose their tracks.

26:51.801 --> 26:53.261
Come on.

26:57.021 --> 26:58.501
Take a look.

27:00.521 --> 27:01.661
Are you fine?

27:03.391 --> 27:04.531
I'm fine.

27:08.801 --> 27:09.941
Let me carry you.

27:15.681 --> 27:17.501
This is so embarrassing.

27:19.351 --> 27:20.491
Watch out.

27:24.761 --> 27:26.541
I'm about to slip off.

27:32.151 --> 27:33.371
Let me light up the path.

27:34.521 --> 27:35.800
Want to see who can run faster,

27:35.801 --> 27:37.981
my bunny or you?

27:43.281 --> 27:44.611
They're gone

27:44.721 --> 27:46.461
- in a blink of an eye.
- Let's look around.

27:55.311 --> 27:57.070
Oh no, she must have seen me.

27:57.071 --> 27:58.910
No, it's so dark,
she couldn't have seen you.

27:58.911 --> 28:00.870
- Don't worry.
- She must have seen me.

28:00.871 --> 28:02.821
Her eyes met mine.

28:03.681 --> 28:05.390
It was just a while.

28:05.391 --> 28:07.150
I guess they didn't see us.

28:07.151 --> 28:08.291
Right?

28:08.871 --> 28:10.011
What's wrong?

28:11.961 --> 28:13.131
Officer Chen?

28:15.151 --> 28:16.040
No,

28:16.041 --> 28:17.590
we're not supposed to go there.

28:17.591 --> 28:19.891
We need to go back, not this way.

28:21.111 --> 28:22.251
This is the right way.

28:38.831 --> 28:41.061
Your Lordship, Your Ladyship.

28:42.001 --> 28:43.341
Ms. Zhao sprained her ankle.

28:44.831 --> 28:46.821
I will take her home safely.

28:47.401 --> 28:48.711
Don't worry.

28:52.761 --> 28:53.901
Zhangru.

28:54.071 --> 28:55.651
Be careful.

28:56.831 --> 28:58.021
Ms. Longevity.

29:08.001 --> 29:09.171
No matter what,

29:09.391 --> 29:11.781
it's responsible of Chen Jia
to show himself

29:12.311 --> 29:13.691
and explain to us.

29:16.501 --> 29:18.001
Shall we continue following them?

29:18.941 --> 29:20.081
No.

29:33.461 --> 29:34.641
Then, can we finally

29:34.861 --> 29:37.121
enjoy the rest of the lantern parade?

30:01.821 --> 30:02.961
Second Young Master.

30:09.861 --> 30:11.001
Miss Miao.

30:12.631 --> 30:13.820
I got this lantern for you

30:13.821 --> 30:15.371
from the lantern parade.

30:15.491 --> 30:17.221
Tonight is the Mid-Autumn Festival.

30:17.361 --> 30:18.931
Why aren't you celebrating?

30:22.141 --> 30:23.281
Mid-Autumn Festival?

30:25.661 --> 30:26.881
There's no one else left

30:27.141 --> 30:28.521
whom I can reunite with now.

30:36.801 --> 30:38.590
These are freshly made Dingsheng cakes.

30:38.591 --> 30:40.161
There's peanuts inside.

30:40.441 --> 30:42.411
I left some for you.

30:43.701 --> 30:46.560
It's tradition to eat cakes
duing the Mid-Autumn Festival

30:46.561 --> 30:48.401
to usher joy and happiness.

30:50.981 --> 30:52.201
Thank you, Miss Miao.

30:52.661 --> 30:53.801
However,

30:54.501 --> 30:55.801
joy and happiness

30:56.781 --> 30:58.041
is beyond my reach now.

31:02.261 --> 31:03.401
Young Master.

31:03.821 --> 31:06.681
You need to forge your path
one step at a time.

31:07.261 --> 31:10.460
When my family experienced its downfall,

31:10.461 --> 31:11.780
all of us

31:11.781 --> 31:13.420
held on together

31:13.421 --> 31:15.641
and survived through
the hardest moments.

31:16.141 --> 31:17.881
Things will get better.

31:22.341 --> 31:23.481
Try one.

31:43.251 --> 31:44.401
That's right.

31:45.081 --> 31:48.041
The hardest moments are over.

31:48.451 --> 31:49.881
Thank you, Miss Miao.

31:50.141 --> 31:52.520
You always comfort me when I feel down.

31:52.521 --> 31:55.361
I don't know how to repay you.

31:57.071 --> 31:59.860
When you handed me the cakes,
I noticed your hands were cold.

31:59.861 --> 32:01.001
Here you go.

32:05.301 --> 32:06.860
If chatting with me

32:06.861 --> 32:08.681
makes you feel better,

32:08.821 --> 32:10.281
that makes me glad.

32:10.741 --> 32:14.481
Perhaps it's just small talk to you,

32:15.501 --> 32:16.681
but to me,

32:17.281 --> 32:18.801
you're a lifesaver.

32:24.061 --> 32:25.561
I can't keep hiding anymore.

32:26.621 --> 32:28.201
I need to leave this courtyard

32:29.781 --> 32:31.321
and live like a man,

32:31.941 --> 32:33.481
forging my own path.

32:36.461 --> 32:37.601
Look.

32:37.861 --> 32:39.121
The moon is beautiful

32:39.621 --> 32:41.841
when it's quiet.

32:42.981 --> 32:44.121
Yes.

32:45.981 --> 32:47.721
I remember a poem

32:48.171 --> 32:50.441
about moons and bamboos.

32:50.781 --> 32:52.490
What was it again?

32:52.491 --> 32:53.881
"Is there ever a night

32:54.341 --> 32:55.721
with no moon and bamboo groves?

32:56.301 --> 32:58.921
But there is definitely
a dearth of idlers like us two."

32:58.941 --> 33:00.081
Correct?

33:00.371 --> 33:01.511
Yes.

33:25.901 --> 33:29.121
(Harmonious Nature)

33:48.111 --> 33:49.251
Ms. Longevity.

33:52.651 --> 33:55.081
Ms. Longevity, why are you crying?

34:00.501 --> 34:01.881
The antidote

34:02.501 --> 34:05.681
can only suppress
the poison temporarily.

34:05.821 --> 34:06.961
It does not cure it.

34:07.511 --> 34:09.361
It can only prolong
your life for a while.

34:13.901 --> 34:15.081
It's fine.

34:15.341 --> 34:16.260
See?

34:16.261 --> 34:17.881
I'm still alive and well.

34:17.981 --> 34:18.980
Besides,

34:18.981 --> 34:21.271
it's possible that the poison
might just stay dormant.

34:22.771 --> 34:24.101
There must be a way.

34:25.491 --> 34:26.631
Don't cry.

34:32.821 --> 34:35.001
(Liaodong)

34:44.771 --> 34:46.420
Your Highness,
you haven't missed a shot.

34:46.421 --> 34:47.680
You're definitely

34:47.681 --> 34:50.401
one of the best archers in the kingdom.

34:51.901 --> 34:54.220
You Song brothers are interesting.

34:54.221 --> 34:56.761
One of you kept rejecting my offers,

34:57.501 --> 35:00.441
while the other came all the way here

35:00.551 --> 35:02.481
just to flatter me.

35:04.421 --> 35:08.241
My brother and father
didn't appreciate your offer,

35:08.341 --> 35:10.961
but I do.

35:12.181 --> 35:14.241
I do not like incapable men,

35:17.381 --> 35:18.521
and I absolutely detest

35:20.031 --> 35:21.361
those who are disloyal.

35:25.061 --> 35:27.781
In the past, I had no choice.

35:28.261 --> 35:29.441
But now,

35:30.221 --> 35:31.681
I want to make my own choice.

35:32.021 --> 35:34.351
I don't want to spend my life
feeling inferior to someone.

35:34.981 --> 35:36.700
All I need is an opportunity,

35:36.701 --> 35:38.681
and I shall repay you in ways

35:38.921 --> 35:40.321
that exceed what Song Mo can offer.

35:42.741 --> 35:43.881
Pray tell.

35:46.021 --> 35:47.451
While you were practicing earlier,

35:47.461 --> 35:49.891
you released your arrow even before
you pulled it all the way back.

35:50.231 --> 35:53.241
That's because you're used to practicing
with the same equipment,

35:53.541 --> 35:56.250
and you know where the arrow will land.

35:56.251 --> 35:57.660
However, in the battlefield,

35:57.661 --> 35:59.721
nothing is certain.

36:00.161 --> 36:04.221
I suggest that you
need a practice partner

36:04.341 --> 36:06.001
to train your adaptability skills.

36:06.181 --> 36:09.121
That will improve your archery, too.

36:11.301 --> 36:12.801
But if I accidentally shoot you,

36:13.541 --> 36:15.721
it'd be bad for my reputation.

36:17.981 --> 36:20.281
If your real target is Song Mo,

36:20.931 --> 36:23.521
I'd be the perfect training partner.

36:24.541 --> 36:25.690
Compared to a mere servant,

36:25.691 --> 36:27.010
I have the status

36:27.011 --> 36:28.560
to help you befriend

36:28.561 --> 36:30.361
the younger noblemen and officials.

36:30.521 --> 36:33.380
I also know how to plan strategies
to secure your position in politics

36:33.381 --> 36:34.350
and navigate through uncertainties.

36:34.351 --> 36:37.440
I also know how to fight, and I can make sure
that the capital troops

36:37.441 --> 36:39.681
won't completely fall under
Song Mo's hands.

36:48.981 --> 36:50.561
You sound like

36:51.341 --> 36:53.561
I need you more

36:53.741 --> 36:57.081
than you need me.

37:00.461 --> 37:02.420
If you were to separately evaluate

37:02.421 --> 37:05.321
my background, warriorship,
and scholarship,

37:05.541 --> 37:07.321
I may not be your best choice.

37:07.331 --> 37:08.811
However, I do fulfill
those three criteria,

37:08.821 --> 37:12.001
and more importantly, I have
the determination to fight till I die.

37:14.381 --> 37:15.761
War is all about strategy.

37:17.141 --> 37:20.801
Ever since I was born, I was destined
to thwart Song Mo's plans.

37:21.021 --> 37:22.161
I'm the only person

37:22.201 --> 37:24.641
who can help you secretly

37:24.861 --> 37:26.321
align everyone to your side.

37:37.981 --> 37:40.540
The ministers are planning to organize

37:40.541 --> 37:43.641
a supplementary imperial examination
to search for new talents.

37:44.221 --> 37:46.841
If you can pass
the initial examinations,

37:47.341 --> 37:50.041
I will take you in.

37:51.461 --> 37:52.761
Thank you, Your Highness.

38:01.581 --> 38:02.721
Master Ji.

38:04.821 --> 38:06.540
Song Han came to me with an offer,

38:06.541 --> 38:08.161
just as you predicted.

38:08.461 --> 38:10.161
You are truly an oracle.

38:10.341 --> 38:11.761
It's just a strategical deduction.

38:12.181 --> 38:13.841
Song Han is now desperate,

38:13.901 --> 38:15.921
and if he doesn't get
to grow into a mighty wolf,

38:15.941 --> 38:17.660
given his paranoid nature,

38:17.661 --> 38:20.561
he'd have to live in fear and guilt.

38:20.701 --> 38:23.441
By then, life would
torture him to the core.

38:25.541 --> 38:28.761
Song Han's situation
is actually similar to mine.

38:29.091 --> 38:31.871
In the Song family,
no matter how capable he is,

38:32.141 --> 38:34.321
Song Mo will always outdo him.

38:34.751 --> 38:37.671
After all, nothing can change the fact
that he was an illicit love child.

38:38.221 --> 38:40.721
His only choice is to help me
claim the throne

38:41.661 --> 38:44.681
so that he can stand tall in the future.

38:45.301 --> 38:47.641
Master Ji, you're truly
a far-sighted strategist.

38:53.101 --> 38:54.481
Here's a token of my appreciation.

39:10.101 --> 39:12.601
Just seeing them carrying these chests
makes me feel exhausted.

39:13.461 --> 39:15.201
Why do I need so much money?

39:18.421 --> 39:19.500
Forget it.

39:19.501 --> 39:20.841
Where are you going, Master Ji?

39:21.221 --> 39:22.361
Back to the capital.

39:23.901 --> 39:25.690
At first, I wanted to help you

39:25.691 --> 39:27.400
since the Empress supports you,

39:27.401 --> 39:29.350
and you were so eager to learn.

39:29.351 --> 39:30.491
But now,

39:30.501 --> 39:32.440
you're repaying me
with flattery and gold,

39:32.441 --> 39:34.020
without a hint of truth.

39:34.021 --> 39:35.881
Why should I waste my time?

39:36.021 --> 39:37.161
If you want to end my life,

39:37.221 --> 39:38.601
get someone to come with me.

39:39.221 --> 39:40.361
Wait, Master Ji.

39:47.181 --> 39:49.761
I treat you with utmost sincerity.

39:51.541 --> 39:53.081
Utmost sincerity?

39:53.821 --> 39:55.460
How did the Duke of Ding die?

39:55.461 --> 39:56.961
You refused to mention a word of it.

39:59.221 --> 40:00.881
Working for a sly and paranoid man

40:01.101 --> 40:04.321
will only ruin my elaborate plans.

40:04.771 --> 40:06.161
I understand, Master Ji.

40:06.301 --> 40:08.281
I will tell you everything
about the Duke of Ding,

40:08.801 --> 40:10.521
from the beginning till the end.

40:11.001 --> 40:12.601
When I eventually succeed,

40:13.141 --> 40:15.001
you will be my top adviser.

40:16.781 --> 40:18.201
Is that what

40:18.541 --> 40:20.961
you promised Dou Shishu, too?

40:22.711 --> 40:24.180
Both you and Dou Shishu

40:24.181 --> 40:25.921
are my right-hand men.

40:26.501 --> 40:27.540
However,

40:27.541 --> 40:30.001
Dou Shishu offered his horse market
to show his sincerity,

40:30.021 --> 40:31.601
and he's willing to sacrifice his niece.

40:32.491 --> 40:34.081
As for you,

40:34.171 --> 40:36.481
you still haven't helped me
gain Song Mo's support.

40:38.181 --> 40:39.361
Song Mo?

40:39.741 --> 40:41.841
He's loyal to the Emperor.

40:42.421 --> 40:43.681
If I recruit him,

40:44.021 --> 40:45.961
I'd be opposing the Emperor directly.

40:46.581 --> 40:48.441
You think the Emperor
would let me do that?

40:49.221 --> 40:50.841
What would you do by then?

40:51.381 --> 40:53.961
Start a coup in Liaodong,
which is thousands of lis away?

40:54.741 --> 40:56.081
Are you certain about that?

40:56.101 --> 40:57.281
But if we don't eliminate him,

40:57.541 --> 40:59.010
he'd be a threat.

40:59.011 --> 41:01.221
The Imperial Guards are elite soldiers
that defend the palace.

41:01.241 --> 41:03.100
We have to seize control of them.

41:03.101 --> 41:04.441
That's why

41:06.221 --> 41:09.321
I'm asking you to recruit
Song Han instead.

41:09.911 --> 41:11.580
Since we can't recruit
the Songs publicly,

41:11.581 --> 41:13.391
we can take advantage
of their family issues.

41:13.561 --> 41:14.660
Song Han wants his dukeship.

41:14.661 --> 41:16.291
He's at loggerheads
with his brother now.

41:16.301 --> 41:19.180
That's between him and his brother.

41:19.181 --> 41:20.620
No matter how things develop,

41:20.621 --> 41:21.700
it will only benefit you,

41:21.701 --> 41:23.001
and this is a guaranteed result.

41:26.381 --> 41:27.641
I understand.

41:28.581 --> 41:30.361
The ice cream tastes good.

41:40.541 --> 41:43.521
(Lu's Dental Clinic)

41:51.021 --> 41:53.260
Song Han is just an illicit love child.

41:53.261 --> 41:54.620
You're recruiting him?

41:54.621 --> 41:57.281
I think he has
a special position to play.

41:57.341 --> 41:58.801
If we use him well,

41:58.821 --> 42:01.801
we can turn the tide.

42:02.541 --> 42:06.201
He's a lowly man with high ambitions.

42:06.941 --> 42:08.161
A man like him

42:09.181 --> 42:11.641
is more likely to heed our bidding.

42:17.941 --> 42:19.081
I lose.

42:21.381 --> 42:23.281
Minister Lu, did you lose to me,

42:23.981 --> 42:25.481
so you can ask me for a favor?

42:26.061 --> 42:27.561
To be honest,

42:27.981 --> 42:30.841
I don't think my son will pass
the normal imperial examinations.

42:30.901 --> 42:32.881
As for the upcoming
supplementary imperial examinations,

42:32.901 --> 42:35.521
we still need some help.

42:35.721 --> 42:37.721
The palace is in need
of military talents.

42:38.181 --> 42:41.401
His Majesty is taking the
military examinations seriously.

42:41.541 --> 42:43.580
I have been ordered
to appoint another examiner,

42:43.581 --> 42:46.281
and I guess they already
have a candidate in mind,

42:46.821 --> 42:49.041
so I'm afraid I have to disappoint you.

42:52.401 --> 42:55.000
I can't interfere in something
that's beyond my authority.

42:55.001 --> 42:57.031
But you're in charge
of imperial examinations,

42:57.541 --> 42:59.081
so I'm sure you can

42:59.541 --> 43:01.281
do something about it.

43:03.901 --> 43:07.081
For the written examinations,
there's still some room for wriggling.

43:07.141 --> 43:08.641
However, the military examinations

43:08.981 --> 43:10.801
will test their true abilities.

43:11.101 --> 43:12.281
Don't worry, Minister Dou.

43:12.501 --> 43:14.441
As long as he can pass
the written examinations,

43:14.461 --> 43:15.700
I'm sure my son

43:15.701 --> 43:17.361
is good enough

43:17.921 --> 43:19.641
to fight his way through.

43:42.221 --> 43:44.811
I just want to make a name for myself
through my own capabilities,

43:44.821 --> 43:46.060
and you're stopping me?

43:46.061 --> 43:47.140
You might as well kill me

43:47.141 --> 43:48.281
in front of His Majesty.

43:48.541 --> 43:50.460
Mantis Song is now a public enemy.

43:50.461 --> 43:52.180
For your sake and your family's,

43:52.181 --> 43:54.001
you can't take this risk with him.

43:54.261 --> 43:55.401
Leave him.

43:57.741 --> 44:00.401
♪The golden fiery steed
rides across the vast horizon♪

44:01.021 --> 44:04.121
♪In this life, oh♪

44:04.261 --> 44:05.940
♪Without you♪

44:05.941 --> 44:09.561
♪What is there to envy?♪

44:10.021 --> 44:12.500
♪Let me lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

44:12.501 --> 44:16.820
♪To adorn your hair with a jade hairpin♪

44:16.821 --> 44:19.020
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

44:19.021 --> 44:23.441
♪Bloom in a single night for you♪

44:23.621 --> 44:26.740
♪The splendor of the world is
but fleeting sorrow♪

44:26.741 --> 44:29.841
♪Should the flames of war arise♪

44:30.181 --> 44:33.420
♪I shall hold your hand♪

44:33.421 --> 44:36.380
♪And walk through the dust♪

44:36.381 --> 44:38.620
♪I want to hold you in my arms♪

44:38.621 --> 44:42.900
♪Leaving the world behind♪

44:42.901 --> 44:45.220
♪From now on,
all the vast wonders of the world♪

44:45.221 --> 44:49.460
♪May be left as blank spaces♪

44:49.461 --> 44:53.161
♪The dazzling spring moon over the city♪

44:53.341 --> 44:56.401
♪Is no match for your beauty♪

44:56.581 --> 45:01.761
♪Why ascend to high towers again?♪

45:02.581 --> 45:04.820
♪I will lay down my blade
and leave the sea of battles♪

45:04.821 --> 45:06.460
♪Break my spear to crown you♪

45:06.461 --> 45:09.180
♪With a golden-branch hairpin♪

45:09.181 --> 45:11.300
♪Let a thousand, ten thousand blossoms♪

45:11.301 --> 45:15.420
♪Bloom for you♪

45:15.421 --> 45:19.201
♪No more guarding lonely towers♪

45:19.221 --> 45:22.540
♪Spring is near, ripe for the taking♪

45:22.541 --> 45:23.900
♪Holding your hand♪

45:23.901 --> 45:28.841
♪Till we reach beyond the noise♪

45:29.261 --> 45:32.441
♪Only for you, I shall paint♪

45:32.621 --> 45:35.401
♪With bold strokes and vibrant colors♪

45:35.581 --> 45:37.460
♪And for all else♪

45:37.461 --> 45:44.441
♪Let it remain pale and void♪

45:46.901 --> 45:47.940
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama.)

45:47.941 --> 45:48.940
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:48.941 --> 45:50.121
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home.)
